| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0482 — Recovery Inhibition (m3rx)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 03a6a4da-4b05-5d3d-be5f-c3e67f9dd431"
